snippet.title: Session Announce Trailer
snippet.description: Heavily inspired by the golden era and skate culture of the late 90s/early 2000s, Project: Session is all about authenticity and creativity. Freedom of expression is the core of skateboarding so players shouldn't have to worry about how many point their tricks are worth. Instead, Session offers a unique control scheme that gives players full control.
